asset.author: iRobot

transcripts: Debris extractors should be cleaned every four months. Pinch the yellow extractor frame release tabs, then lift up the extractor frame and remove any obstructions. Remove the debris extractors in the yellow debris extractor caps. Remove any hair or debris that has collected underneath the caps and around the metal axles. Remove hair and debris from the plastic pegs on the other side of the debris extractors. Replace the debris extractors into the frame and close the frame
